      "review_summary": "This PR registers Swedish (`sv`) as a lazy Control UI locale, adds generated Swedish locale assets and metadata, updates language labels across existing locale bundles, and adds registry tests for `sv-SE` detection.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR blocker: source inspection of the PR head shows `sv.meta.json` includes `login.failure.*` fallback keys and only 802/1118 translated keys. This is a source-reproducible merge-readiness issue, not a current-main runtime bug.",
